{"id":29762662686,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAG7f4xHg","head_branch":"fix/DHIS2-21860-userrole-usergroup-members-projection","head_sha":"aaaa59d80ee1ec62d16d59e400ffa80e0ecd6eb9","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":51249,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"fix: avoid full User materialization for userRole/userGroup members projection [DHIS2-21860]","status":"completed","conclusion":"failure","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":80597177735,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAASw_dVhw","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29762662686","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29762662686","pull_requests":[{"id":4093009643,"number":24512,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/24512","head":{"ref":"fix/DHIS2-21860-userrole-usergroup-members-projection","sha":"5f88670f24da82f7fb46e43e72618979330c2b8a","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"master","sha":"e4a9688cf130fe90449711315803683fd8851ae5","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-07-20T17:10:43Z","updated_at":"2026-07-20T17:21:26Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-20T17:10:43Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29762662686/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29762662686/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/80597177735","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29762662686/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29762662686/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29762662686/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix: avoid full User materialization for userRole/userGroup members projection [DHIS2-21860]\n\nGET /api/userRoles/{id}?fields=users[*] and the equivalent userGroups\nendpoint forced Hibernate to fully materialize every member User (and\neach of their own associations) just to serialize a handful of summary\nfields. On a role with ~83k members this meant 500k+ queries and 90s+\nresponse times.\n\n- UserRoleStore/UserGroupStore gain getUserSummaries(UID), a raw SQL\n  projection (uid, code, username, firstName, surname, name) via a new\n  UserSummaryRowMapper, bypassing the ORM entirely.\n- UserRole/UserGroup expose a transient userSummaries override that\n  getUsers()/getMembers() prefer when set, leaving every other caller\n  (real Hibernate lifecycle, business logic) unaffected.\n- FieldFilterService.applyUserSummaries installs the projection only\n  when \"users\" is requested, checked directly against the field-path\n  list rather than via the generic per-leaf field-path visitor used by\n  applyAccess/applySharingDisplayNames -- that visitor processes each\n  requested leaf (users.groups, users.organisationUnits, ...) as an\n  independent, unordered walk from the root, so a leaf-based check for\n  the bare \"users\" entry raced against those other leaves and lost\n  more often than not, still materializing the real collection.\n- UserGroup.hbm.xml maps `members` with access=\"field\" so Hibernate's\n  own flush-time dirty-checking bypasses the overridden getter,\n  avoiding a TransientObjectException if a write touches the same\n  managed instance later in the same session.\n- getUserSummaries() flushes the session first, since membership can\n  also change via plain ORM paths (DefaultCollectionService, User's\n  owning-side role assignment) that stay unflushed until Hibernate\n  decides to, which the raw JDBC read would otherwise miss.\n\nA related issue was found but is out of scope here: LinkService still\neagerly loads the full real member collection for href generation\nbefore field-filtering ever runs, independent of this fix.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"aaaa59d80ee1ec62d16d59e400ffa80e0ecd6eb9","tree_id":"4ea6a21566e8a02a1e40a666196194e2f4f8c10c","timestamp":"2026-07-20T17:09:33Z","committer":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the service layer and Web API.","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core","fork":false,"private":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core","archive_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/{archive_format}{/ref}","assignees_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/assignees{/user}","blobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/git/blobs{/sha}","branches_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/branches{/branch}","collaborators_url":"https://ap